high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the round wooden table.
Pick up the dirty grey plate with the sponge on it off of the wooden table.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the dirty grey plate with the sponge on it into the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean plate and sponge.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk over to the round wooden table.
Put the clean grey plate with the sponge on it onto the round wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean grey plate with a sponge on it on a round wooden table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the door, turn left, and walk to the table.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and pick up the plate.
Turn right, walk to the counter, turn right, and walk to the table.
Put the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate with a clean sponge on it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the dirty plate that's in front of you.
Turn left and take a step to your left and then walk to the sink.
Wash the plate in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the table then take a small step to your left.
Put the plate back where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate on the table.
